    <a title="Adriana Sveen" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/66598084-adriana-sveen"><img alt="Adriana Sveen" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1491322893p2/66598084.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
