<span id="freeTextContainer13031066973862104299">Amelie Nothomb never disappoints! And her translator does a superb job. This short novel describes a reality tv show called Concentration, where the participants are rounded up, put in a camp, starved, beaten, and worked to death. The show is incredibly successful with viewers. <br/><br/>A horrifying premise.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


