        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2712669583" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12361607710841484022">3,5/5<br/>This was pretty interesting, and quite realistic, but I did feel like the ending was rushed. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


